# John Kiriakou Interactive Site Rules

- Use a modern React + Vite architecture with Tailwind CSS and shadcn/ui patterns.
- Keep event/location data in `src/data/locations.ts`.
- Maintain a real 3D globe experience (Three.js) with route arcs and selectable points.
- Preserve high visual quality, accessibility, and responsive behavior.
- Keep source links for any biographical or historical detail changes.
